---
title: Garden Mushroom-Stuffed Ravioli with Zucchini Ribbons, Tomato & Creamy Lemon Sauce
description: Tender ravioli are pretty much good in any form, but they’re especially great when packed with fresh mushroom and creamy cheese. This rendition is “dragged through the garden,” majorly amping up the veggie factor. Yep, this delicious dish is loaded with chopped and ribboned zucchini, diced tomato, and a bevvy of Italian herbs and spices. It’s taken to the next level with a creamy lemon sauce, nutty Parmesan, and a sprinkle of scallion greens. Be still, our pasta-loving hearts…
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garden-mushroom-stuffed-ravioli-5030a54a.jpg
